      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" draggable=\"true\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL\"> Stellar Revelation</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div title=\"Page 55\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>You can cause your melee weapon to exert a gravitational pull, drawing strikes to meet it. If a creature hits you or a creature adjacent to you with a melee attack and you&rsquo;re wielding a melee weapon, you can make a melee attack roll against the attacking creature as a reaction. If your attack exceeds the attacking creature&rsquo;s KAC + 8, you don&rsquo;t deal damage; instead, the target&rsquo;s attack deals only half damage.</p>\n<p>When you are attuned or fully attuned, you gain a +4 bonus to your attack roll to use this revelation.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
